  <brief_title>Effect of Oral Cinnamon Intervention in Metabolic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Intervention With Oral Cinnamon on Metabolic Profile and Body Composition of Asian Indians With Metabolic Syndrome in North India: A 16 Week Double Blind Placebo Control Trial</official_title>
