  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This double blind placebo control study with supplementation of oral Cinnamon is being
      conducted to test the hypothesis that in subjects with Metabolic Syndrome oral cinnamon may
      lead to improvement in body composition and metabolic parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
